Home Shopping Network Inc filed withthe Securities and Exchange Commission for an offering of 400mln dlrs of convertible subordinated debentures due April 1,2002.    Proceeds from the offering will be used to build and equipenlarged broadcast and order processing facilities, to redeemsome of the company's 11-3/4 pct senior notes due Oct 15, 1996and for general corporate purposes, the company said.    Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc will underwrite the sale. Reuter&#3;